{"serial": "11023", "department_serial": 12, "code": "CL0201", "class": "M", "name": {"en": "Chinese (B): Chinese writing", "ch": "國文（B）：中文寫作"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "密碼卡限僑生高級組領取。 本堂課不開放旁聽"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Li,Xin-Lun"], "ch": ["李欣倫"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "A", "room": "109"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 29, "department": {"ch": "中國文學系", "en": "Department of Chinese Literature"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 29, "remark": {"ch": "密碼卡限僑生高級組領取。 本堂課不開放旁聽", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程將透過閱讀作品，教師示範寫作方法，實際帶領同學練習寫作實務，包括：履歷表、企畫書、論文摘要及關鍵字、書評等，並閱讀並分析當代文學作品寫作技巧。", "en": "In this course, students will read works, demonstrate writing methods, and practice writing practices, including resumes, portfolios, essay summaries and key words, and book reviews, as well as read and analyze writing techniques for contemporary literature"}, "outline": {"ch": "週次課程內容備註\n1 課程內容說明\n2    【單元：企劃】\n從終點檢視我的起點：湯姆．尼可斯（Tom Nichols）〈那神奇的七年〉＋企劃書的發想\n3【單元：企劃】\n蔣勳〈生活美學的起點〉+企劃書格式介紹\n4【單元：企劃】\n企劃書格式介紹＋實戰寫作「企劃書」\n5【單元：企劃】企劃書實戰寫作與發表\n6【單元：文學】讀書心得、書介到書評的撰寫格式與內容介紹／練習分析文本：謝旺霖〈因為我懷疑〉\n7.課堂撰寫讀書心得\n8【單元：企劃】讀書心得小組互評、佳作欣賞\n9.論文寫作概說\n10問題意識＋摘要＋研究動機＋研究方法＋參考文獻\n練習分析文本／手機控必讀：吳修銘〈智慧型手機與另類自戀〉\n11.摘要寫作與下標題練習\n詹姆斯．克利爾（James Clear）《原子習慣：細微改變帶來巨大成就的細微改革》摘要寫作與下標題練習\n12【單元：自述（自傳篇）】\n練習分析文本／假新聞與後真相：讀海特．麥當娜《後真相時代》段落選讀\n13【單元：自述（自傳篇）】練習分析文本／假新聞與後真相：讀海特．麥當娜《後真相時代\n14【單元：自述（自傳篇）】\n「我是誰？」：從自傳、自述到自我書寫的形式區隔與內容介紹\n15【單元：新聞】\n閱讀媒體：阿潑〈災難與媒體〉深度人物採訪報導人物採訪應避免的地雷＋你應該知道的事\n不要再惹毛受訪者了：讀「小小書房」和「有河」公告信\n16【單元：文學＋自述】\n故事分析之小組報告\n17【單元：新聞＋文學＋自述】\n「報導者」人物採訪專題報導\n18.期末回饋", "en": "1 Course Description Grouping\n2 Reading article about “How to become a university student“\n3 Project Writing\n4 Project Writing\n5 Project Writing and Presentation\n6.Book Review Writing\n7.Book Review Writing\n8.Group Reviews\n9.Introduction to Academic Essay Writing\n10.Introduction to Academic Essay Writing\n11-13.Abstract Writing\n14-15.People Interviews\n16-17.Resume Writing\n18.Final Classroom Feedback"}, "textbook": {"ch": "傑克‧哈特（Jack Hart），《說故事的技藝》（新北：新樂園出版/遠足文化事業股份有限公司，2020年）。", "en": "Jack Hart, The Art of Storytelling (Xinbei: New Paradise Publishing/Farfoot Culture Co., Ltd., 2020)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1.課堂發言：20％（一次五分）\n2.書評寫作：15％\n3.課堂學習單：40％\n4.企劃書：15％\n5.口頭報告：10％", "en": "1. Class Participation: 20％ \n2. Book review: 15％\n3. Classroom study list: 40％\n4. Project proposal: 15％\n5. Oral report: 10％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三下午1:00-5:00", "en": "Wed. 13:00-17:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "最後兩週讓同學回饋課程或是補考", "en": "Final Classroom Feedback"}, "domain": {"ch": "現當代文學\n\n\n、\n\n\n應用中文", "en": "現當代文學\n\n\n、\n\n\n應用中文"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "文獻解讀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯思辨", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "語文表達", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "文學鑑賞", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "人文素養與國際視野", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作品/創作展演"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Interpreting classics", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Logical thinking", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Language communication", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Appreciation of literature", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Humanistic and international outlook", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Products/Creative Performance"]}]}, "assignCriteria": {"ch"